{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Your death was just the beginning</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Grim Reaper has secrets to share about your untimely demise. Nothing is as it seems, and your death was far from natural.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662330/extras/divider_1_.png?t=1733390995\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Listen</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into a medieval audio drama brought to life by a cast of professional voice actors, including Neil Bell (<i>Dune</i>, <i>Peaky Blinders</i>). Immerse yourself in an intricate web of character-driven storylines that unfold simultaneously. Uncover clues that may either guide you or mislead you\u2014it\u2019s up to you to discern the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662330/extras/divider_1_.png?t=1733390995\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Solve</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As an unseen spectre, you\u2019ll explore pivotal moments frozen in time, seeking answers to pressing questions. Each revelation unravels a piece of a larger, interconnected mystery\u2014one that ties directly to your own fate.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662330/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733390995","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662330/page.bg.jpg?t=1733390995","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662330/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733390995","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2662330/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733390995","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family S